# Contact form delivery endpoint.
# LEAVE THIS UNSET in dev/staging — the contact form stays in stub mode and
# nothing is delivered to the live business inbox.
#
# To GO LIVE in production, copy this file to .env.production (or set the var
# in your host's environment) and point it at a form backend that accepts a
# JSON POST, e.g.:
#   - Formspree:  https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id
#   - Web3Forms:  https://api.web3forms.com/submit  (also add your access_key)
#   - or your own endpoint
#
# VITE_FORM_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id
